## Title
Xubuntu

## URL
http://xubuntu.org

## Description
Based on Ubuntu, great online support, huge community.
Uses the Xfce desktop environment which is traditional and lightweight.

## Pros
 - Ubuntu based
 - Very lightweight UI
 - Simple yet powerful configuration
 - Works great on older hardware

## Cons
 - Xfce, the default DE, isn't as polished

